\nthe issue of limit cycles in theories with a global symmetry and it is shown\nhow this sheds new light on the geometry of the space of couplings in QFT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2016 16:34:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 8 Apr 2017 19:40:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-11"}
