 with existing inexact approaches, i.e. the ones which do not\nnecessarily identify the minimum FSM, and these comparisons show encouraging\nresults.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 09:34:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Nov 2016 18:34:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-22"}
