 CO emission suggests that the source is\nyounger than 1000 years. The mass, momentum, momentum rate, mechanical\nluminosity, kinetic energy and mass-loss rate are also all estimated to be low.\nA full 3D radiative transfer model of the system can explain all the\nkinematical and morphological features in the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2016 09:38:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-09"}
